    "summary": "The user asks for an overview of antitrust investigations into Big Tech, then follows up with probing questions about the strength of the regulators' cases and the likelihood of meaningful reform. The assistant provides balanced summaries of both the regulatory/critical perspective and the tech companies' counterarguments throughout the conversation.",
